{"word":"Dove, Turtle","slug":"dove,-turtle","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Dove, Turtle</b> Sent out from the ark by Noah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=8&verse=11'>Gen 8:11</a><br/> Mourning of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=38&verse=14'>Isa 38:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=59&verse=11'>Isa 59:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=34&chapter=2&verse=7'>Nah 2:7</a><br/> Domesticated<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=60&verse=8'>Isa 60:8</a><br/> Nests of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=48&verse=28'>Jer 48:28</a><br/> Harmlessness of, typical of Christ's gentleness<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=10&verse=16'>Mat 10:16</a><br/> Sacrificial uses of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=15&verse=9'>Gen 15:9</a><br/> Prescribed for purification:<br/> - Of women<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=12&verse=6'>Lev 12:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=12&verse=8'>Lev 12:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=24'>Luk 2:24</a> <br/> - Of Nazarites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=6&verse=10'>Num 6:10</a> <br/> - Of lepers<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=14&verse=22'>Lev 14:22</a> <br/> Burnt offering of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=1&verse=17'>Lev 1:17</a><br/> Trespass offering of, for the impecunious<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=5&verse=10'>Lev 5:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=12&verse=8'>Lev 12:8</a><br/> Sin offering, for those who touched any dead body<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=6&verse=10'>Num 6:10</a><br/> Market for, in the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=21&verse=12'>Mat 21:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=2&verse=14'>Joh 2:14</a><br/> Symbolic of the Holy Spirit<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=3&verse=16'>Mat 3:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=3&verse=22'>Luk 3:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=1&verse=32'>Joh 1:32</a><br/><a href='S:Pigeon'>Pigeon</a>"}]}